@node @code{ledger-mode-extras-currencies}
@section @code{ledger-mode-extras-currencies}

@vindex ledger-mode-extras-currencies
The user option @code{ledger-mode-extras-currencies} is a list of currency
symbols (strings) for which price information should be fetched.  This
list is consumed by the external Python scripts invoked by the price
update commands (@ref{Price updates}).  The type is a list of strings.  The
default value is an empty list.

